}Page Hill Middle School conducted a school survey using the following questions: Do you attend a religious meeting a)regularly,b)occasionally or c)not at all? Where is the meeting held? Results were: 42 people attended Buckingham & Village CofE churches. 2 attended the Salvation Army. 2 attended the Methodist Church. 4 attended the Pentecostal Church. 5 attended St. Bernadines. 15 attended other Village Churches.
13% attended meetings regularly,27% attended occasionally,and 59% did not attend meetings.
